  lines:
  - speakerName: Lamp
    portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 61ce7f18f680f0d409ce1a814d48b7cf, type: 3}
    text: What? The kids still say that, right?
  - speakerName: You
    portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 787fafedeaa52fc4a96a9263c592c76e, type: 3}
    text: "No. They really don\u2019t."
  - speakerName: Lamp
    portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 61ce7f18f680f0d409ce1a814d48b7cf, type: 3}
    text: Okay, Epic bacon!
  - speakerName: You
    portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 787fafedeaa52fc4a96a9263c592c76e, type: 3}
    text: Omg... that's even worse
  - speakerName: Lamp
    portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 4cc0f77cf054ed340b8f3f30720d91ce, type: 3}
    text: Fine. It was lit.
  - speakerName: You
    portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 787fafedeaa52fc4a96a9263c592c76e, type: 3}
    text: Please stop
  - speakerName: Lamp
    portrait: {fileID: 21300000, guid: 1cf2efdbf19bab6468e7b31e8a9a4551, type: 3}
    text: Then what do kids say now?
